      <abstract>
        <p>A new Schiff base, 4-[(2-hydroxy-4-pentadecyl-benzylidene)-amino]-benzoic acid methyl ester was synthesized and its UV, IR, <sup>1</sup>H-NMR, <sup>13</sup>C-NMR and ESI-MS spectroscopic data are presented.</p>
      </abstract>
